data.name: PrintSettings
desc: provides access to the settings for printing documents.
These settings are printer independent but affect the rendering of the document.

properties.name: PrintBlackFonts
desc: If TRUE, all characters are printed in black.
It is useful for printing colored text on a b/w printer.

properties.name: PrintControls
desc: If TRUE, control shapes are included in printing.

properties.name: PrintDrawings
desc: If TRUE, drawing objects (shapes) are included in printing.

properties.name: PrintGraphics
desc: If TRUE, graphic objects are included in printing.

properties.name: PrintLeftPages
desc: If TRUE, left pages are included in printing.

properties.name: PrintPageBackground
desc: If TRUE, the background of the page is printed.

properties.name: PrintProspect
desc: If TRUE, the pages are printed in the order of prospects.

properties.name: PrintReversed
desc: If TRUE, the pages are printed in reverse order.
The last page is printed first.

properties.name: PrintRightPages
desc: If TRUE, right pages are included in printing.

properties.name: PrintTables
desc: If TRUE, tables are included in printing.
